\end_inset

 Now, however, we will specify a particular 
\begin_inset Formula $\psi_{0}(x)$
\end_inset

 and find the 
\begin_inset Formula $V(x)$
\end_inset

 that gives 
\begin_inset Formula $\psi(x)\approx\psi_{0}(x)$
\end_inset

