\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\end_inset

 giving a projection operator 
\begin_inset Formula $P=1-\ps\ps^{T}$
\end_inset

 (or 
\begin_inset Formula $P=1-\ket{\psi}\bra{\psi}$
\end_inset

